elements.description:
NXA Talent is redefining recruitment across logistics and supply chain.

We’re not generalists, we’re specialists. Our consultants bring a combined 44 years of experience and a shared mission: to raise the standard of recruitment across logistics, warehouse management, and supply chain technology.

From WMS experts who implement Manhattan, Blue Yonder (JDA), SAP, and Microsoft Dynamics systems, to logistics leaders driving operations across Europe, we deliver talent solutions that go beyond expectations.

Our partnerships are built on insight, integrity, and long-term impact. Whether it’s permanent, interim, or executive search, we deliver people who transform supply chains.

NXA Talent – a true recruitment partner trusted by the industry leaders shaping the future of logistics

elements.description:
Whether you’re a candidate or a client, we’re on the same journey with you.
We’ll give you the confidence and peace of mind that you’re best placed for success, now and in the future as we've immersed ourselves in the supply chain domain for over 15 years.

Our team is fully committed to helping you succeed and we’ve built a team of industry specialists to support you on your journey.

We provide talent solutions for the Supply Chain, Warehouse Management Systems and Logistics spaces and our service is delivered using years of industry knowledge and an unrivalled professional network.
Our approach is straightforward, personal and allows us to focus on your individual requirements.

elements.description:
ReThink Recruitment is a leading recruitment consultancy that services resourcing needs across a number of industry sectors and locations. Our success is based on the in depth knowledge of these sectors coupled with a passion and commitment to deliver excellent results to our clients and candidates.

ReThink Recruitment is part of Rethink Group, delivering recruitment and talent management services internationally to transform businesses in to higher performing organisations. The Group supports clients across the UK, Europe, Middle East, Asia Pacific and the US.
